The head of the firm is found guilty of tax evasion
The conviction of the Lenin District Court of Cheboxara by the Director of the Land and Law of Vyacheslav Morozov was found guilty of offences under article 199, paragraph 2 (b), of the Criminal Code (failure from paying taxes to the organization by including in the tax declaration known to be false information committed on a particularly large scale) and article 327, paragraph 2, of the Criminal Code (forgering of an official document granting the right and exonerating the duty for the purpose of using it to cover up another crime and facilitate its commission).
This is reported by the Press Service of the SCR Investigation Department for Chuwasa.
From January 2008 to December 2009, Vyacheslav Morozov submitted information on imperfect transactions to the tax records of the GSS.
According to the fake documents, the company incurred additional costs and consequently reduced the amount of value-added taxes and profits of the organization to 11.2 million roubles.
Vyacheslav Morozov was sentenced to 3.5 years ' suspended imprisonment.
